dcron - simple cron daemon

This tool is not ready for use!

info:
Single daemon, single config file. One task per line. Tab is separator.

example:
# min,hour,mday,mon,wday,command
*       *       *       *       *       exec echo minute passed
30      *       *       *       *       exec echo 30 min passed

output:
dcron 18:53 10.05.2014
run: exec echo minute passed
minute passed
dcron 18:54 10.05.2014
run: exec echo minute passed
minute passed
